import React from "react"
import { Row, Col } from "react-bootstrap"
import Navigation from "./Navigation"

const Reacthooksdemo = () => {

   const [count, setCount] = useState(0)

    return (
        <>
            <Row>
                <Navigation />
            </Row>

            <Row>
                <Col></Col>
                <Col>
                    <Row className="mt-5">
                        Counter: 
                    </Row>
                    <Row className="mt-5">

                    </Row>
                    <Row >
                        <button className="loginbutton"
                       
                        >Click here</button>
                    </Row>
                </Col>
                <Col></Col>
            </Row>
        </>
    )
}

export default Reacthooksdemo
